title: Republicans Who Fight Back | Blake Masters
description:
Arizona senator candidate Blake Masters joins the show to discuss everything from how we need to shape the country's future by honoring its past, to the dire need for election integrity, to rebuilding the American family. Take a listen to get a taste of the future of the Republican Party.
